      <div class="prose max-w-none text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-4 text-justify text-sm md:text-base">
        <p>
          <strong>CONSORCIO COMEX, S.A. DE C.V., ALERMAC INVERSIONES, S.A. DE C.V., CONAXE, S.A. DE C.V.; GRUPO COMEX,
